data.name: labelX9.Text
data.value:
Tip: If you do not want to reset you keybindings create a copy of you wow installation and use it for botting

Warning: If you continue without resetting you keybindings the bot may not function correctly.

data.name: labelX4.Text
data.value:
Note: LazyBot does not use Click To Move to navigate the game world. This makes the movement a
bit more unprecise as LazyBot simulates keypresses like if a real player where controlling the character. This do however make LazyBot harder to detect by Warden.

data.name: labelX23.Text
data.value:
LazyBot gives you the option to use a mouse hook.
Mouse hook enables you to use the computer while botting.
If you do not have mouse hook enabled LazyBot will steal you mouse when looting and harvesting.

data.name: labelX22.Text
data.value:
You are now done with the initial setup of the bot and Wow.
You can edit the settings by opening the settings window using the main bot window.
Now please select if you want to Grind (Level) or Gather (Farm):
